    <div class="body">
        <p>On some installations this would make the directory with the specific dirmask
@mkdir($this-&gt;_path(self::_idToFileName($id)), $this-&gt;_options['hashedDirectoryUmask'], true);</p>

<p>because mkdir relays on the umask settings.</p>

<p>Solution:
umask(000) before or a single chmod after this.</p>

